'''Baxri''' ({{lang-en|''Cyan''}}; {{lang-ar|سيان}}) waa [[midab]] [[cagaar]]-[[buluug]] xiga ah.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://dictionary.reference.com/browse/cyan|title=''Cyan'' definition on dictionary.com|work=Dictionary.com|accessdate=30 September 2014}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.merriam-webster.com/dictionary/cyan|title=Cyan - Definition and More from the Free Merriam-Webster Dictionary|publisher=|accessdate=30 September 2014}}</ref><ref>''Shorter Oxford English Dictionary'', 5th Edition, Oxford University Press, 2002.</ref> 

[[File:RGB illumination.jpg|thumb|left|Iskudarka midabada]]
Marka la iskudhex daro sadexda midab ee [[Casaan]]ka, [[Cagaar]]ka iyo [[Buluug]]a ayaa sameeya midabo badan kuwaasi oo ka mid yahay midabkan ''baxriga'' ah. Samayskaas dhexdiisa waxaa midabka baxriga laga helaa buluuga iyo cagaarka dhexdooda. Sidoo kale waxaa midabkan lagu helaa marka la kala goynayo (jarayo) midabada ayadoo la isticmaalayo habka afka qalaad lagu yidhaahdo ''''CMYK color model''', taasi oo midabkani ka soo dhex baxo cagaar, madoow iyo buluug.

Si kastaba ha ahaatee, waa la isku raacay in midabkan la isticmaali jirey tan iyo wakhtiyo aad u horeeyay; waxaana la sheegaa in wakhtigii [[Fircoon|Boqortooyadii Faraaciyiinta]] dhulka [[Masar]] la isticmaali jirey midabkan baxriga ah.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.etymonline.com/index.php?term=cyan|title=Online Etymology Dictionary|publisher=|accessdate=30 September 2014}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.perseus.tufts.edu/hopper/text?doc=Perseus%3Atext%3A1999.04.0057%3Aentry%3Dku%2Fanos|title=Henry George Liddell, Robert Scott,  A Greek-English Lexicon, κύα^νος|publisher=|accessdate=30 September 2014}}</ref> 

Guud ahaan, midabkan waxaa lagu isticmaalo meelo badan; waxaa ka mid ah qalabka wax lagu daabaco (printer), [[Kumbuyuutar]]ka, [[Telefishin]]ka, diiradaha wax lagu sifeeyo iyo meelo kale.
Waxyaabaha ugu cajiibsan ee midabkan waxaa ka mid ah, markuu la [[falgal]]o (lagu daro) midabka [[casaan]]ka waxaa meeshii madoowga ahayd isku bedeshaa cadaan.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://physics.about.com/od/lightoptics/a/vislightspec.htm|title=Visible Light Spectrum - Overview and Chart|author=Andrew Zimmerman Jones|work=About|accessdate=30 September 2014}}</ref>


